Procedure Mausklick(X,Y)
  Menu Off
  Local I
  X=Int(X/8)
  Y=Int(Y/16)+1
  For I=27 To 65
    If Anz%(0,I)+38>X And Anz%(0,I)<X And Anz%(1,I)=Y
      Mreq=I
      @Menue
      Mreq=0
    Endif
  Next I
Return
