Procedure Bildcalc
  Local X,Y,P,B,A$
  Cls
  @Dis1
  @Do_var
  @Full_lut
  Cls
  @Rahmung(0)
  For Y=0 To (W(35)-1)
    For X=0 To (W(34)-1)
      P=(Y*W(34)+X)/2
      B=Asc(Mid$(Urbild$,Int(P),1))
      If P-Int(P)>0.1
        B=(B And 240)/16
      Else
        B=B And 15
      Endif
      @Putpix(X*2,Y*2,2,2,B*16)
    Next X
  Next Y
  @Rahmung(1)
  Repeat
    A$=Inkey$
  Until A$=Chr$(27)
  Cls
  Menu Rollo$()
  @Tx
Return
