Procedure Str_clean(A$)
  Local B$,I
  For I=Len(A$) To 1 Step -1
    B$=Mid$(A$,I,1)
    Exit If B$<>"-" And B$<>" " And B$<>":"
  Next I
  A$=Left$(A$,I)
  If Left$(A$,1)<>"-"
    Rueck$=Left$(A$+"...............",17)
  Else
    Rueck$=A$
  Endif
Return
